f(t,n) := \left(\frac{e^y - e^{-y}}{2y}\right)^n = \left(\frac{\sinh y}{y}\right)^n
\frac{\sinh y}{y} = 1+\frac{1}{6}y^2 + \frac{1}{120}y^4+O(y^5)
\ln(1+x)= x-\frac{1}{2}x^2+\frac{1}{3}x^3-\frac{1}{4}x^4+O(x^5)
\ln f(t,n) = \ln \left(\left(\frac{\sinh y}{y}\right)^n\right) =n \ln \left(\frac{\sinh y}{y}\right)  \approx n \ln \left(1+\frac{1}{6}y^2 + \frac{1}{120}y^4+O(y^5)\right) \approx n  \left(\frac{1}{6}y^2 + O(y^3)\right) =n  \left(\frac{1}{6}t^2\frac{3}{n} + O(n^{-3/2})\right) =\frac{1}{2}t^2 + O(n^{-1/2}) 
